The immunoassay market is dominated by the reagents and kits segment, with the software and services segment being the fastest-growing segment. The enzyme immunoassays segment dominated the immunoassay market, followed by the rapid tests segment. The hospital segment dominated the immunoassay market, followed by the clinical laboratories segment.

North America dominates the immunoassay market due to the rise in global population, which significantly increases the prevalence of chronic conditions. Asia-Pacific is the fastest-growing region in the immunoassay market due to ongoing research and development efforts exploring new drugs, gene therapies, and regenerative medicine approaches.

Key companies profiled in the report include Abbott, Siemens Healthineers, Danaher Corporation (Beckman Coulter), bioMérieux SA, Quidel Corporation, Sysmex Corporation, Ortho Clinical Diagnostics, Bio-Rad Laboratories, Inc., F. Hoffmann-La Roche AG, and Becton, Dickinson, and Company.

The report forecasts revenue growth at global, regional, and country levels and provides an analysis of the latest industry trends in each of the sub-segments from 2019 to 2034. The report is available for purchase at a price of USD 1550.
